'''抗双链DNA抗体'''（{{lang-en|Anti-dsDNA antibodies}}）是[[抗核抗体|抗核抗体]]（Anti-nuclear antibody，ANA）中的一种，其靶标的[[抗原|抗原]]是双链[[DNA|DNA]]。一些血液检测如[[酶联免疫吸附试验|酶联免疫吸附试验]]（ELISA）和[[免疫荧光|免疫荧光]]可在诊断实验室检出抗dsDNA抗体。抗dsDNA抗体在[[全身性紅斑狼瘡|全身性紅斑狼瘡]]（SLE）有很高的诊断相关性，对[[狼瘡性腎炎|狼瘡性腎炎]]的发病机制有重要作用<ref name="pmid10629135">{{cite journal |vauthors=Kavanaugh A, Tomar R, Reveille J, Solomon DH, Homburger HA |title=Guidelines for clinical use of the antinuclear antibody test and tests for specific autoantibodies to nuclear antigens. American College of Pathologists |journal=Arch. Pathol. Lab. Med. |volume=124 |issue=1 |pages=71–81 |date=January 2000 |pmid=10629135 |doi=10.1043/0003-9985(2000)124<0071:GFCUOT>2.0.CO;2 |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_archives-of-pathology-laboratory-medicine_2000-01_124_1/page/71}}</ref><ref name="pmid2312358">{{cite journal |vauthors=Mortensen ES, Fenton KA, Rekvig OP |title=Lupus nephritis: the central role of nucleosomes revealed |journal=Am. J. Pathol. |volume=172 |issue=2 |pages=275–83 |date=February 2008 |pmid=18187568 |pmc=2312358 |doi=10.2353/ajpath.2008.070563 |url=}}</ref>。

